With just a peek of skin here and a peek there, Kendall Jenner's a natural at being sexy without revealing too much. Thanks to strategic styling tricks, the model is never overexposed in her looks, even when she's rocking a crop top. You'll notice Kendall always keeps one part of her outfit modest, whether that's covering up with a coat or wearing longer pants with her sheer top. That's why it works!
